你能够调用以下的API:
[['EducationInvestment.fetch_articles', {'name': 'EducationInvestment.fetch_articles', 'description': 'This function fetches articles on a specific topic.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The topic of the articles, e.g., retirement education investment.'}, {'name': 'count', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of articles to fetch.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'articles', 'description': 'A list of articles matching the topic.'}]}], ['EducationInvestment.get_historical_data', {'name': 'EducationInvestment.get_historical_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical data for educational institutions for a specific year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'year', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The year for which historical data is requested.'}, {'name': 'institutions', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The institutions for which data is requested, e.g., all or specific names.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Historical data for the specified institutions.'}]}], ['EducationInvestment.get_real_time_data', {'name': 'EducationInvestment.get_real_time_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves real-time market data for educational institutions.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institutions', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The institutions for which real-time data is requested, e.g., current or specific names.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'data', 'description': 'Real-time market data for the specified institutions.'}]}], ['EducationInvestment.get_investment_advice', {'name': 'EducationInvestment.get_investment_advice', 'description': 'This function provides investment advice based on institution names.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution_names', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of institution names for which advice is requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Investment advice for the specified institutions.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `EducationInvestment.fetch_articles` 并传入 `topic` 和 `count`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "EducationInvestment.fetch_articles",
    "args": "{'topic': 'retirement education investment', 'count': 5}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
